Foam Pet PyPI Rules
		
		

			"foam_pet" is a mix.
		

	

	
	

		
Originals

		

			The rules for originals is the aggregate of
			the rules that can be found at:
			"./Adoption_Location"
		

	

	
	

		
Laboratory :: Frontend

		

			The "foam_pet" "./sveltnetics_packets" (frontent)   
			rules can be found at:
			./Adoption_Location/frontend_licenses.csv
			./Adoption_Location/frontend_licenses_summary.txt
		

	
	
		
	

		
Laboratory :: Python

		

			The PyPI stuff necessary for "foam_pet" might not be
			attached, but if they are, the rules can be found at:  
			./Laboratory/PyPI_rules_full.json
			PyPI_rules_outline.txt
		

		

			"ventures", "somatic", "Emergency", "biotech", "body_scan",
			"botanist", plus "law_dictionary" licenses or rules can be found
			at those directories.
